### 🔄 Flow xử lý đầy đủ

```
1. createAgentSessionFromServices()
   │
   ├──> resource-loader.ts:loadProjectContextFiles()
   │    └── Load AGENTS.md từ cwd, agentDir, ancestors
   │
   ├──> buildSystemPrompt() (system-prompt.ts)
   │    ├── Base role + tools + guidelines + Pi docs
   │    ├── Context files (AGENTS.md)
