   │
   ├──> AgentSession constructor
   │    └── this.agent = config.agent (từ @mariozechner/pi-ai)
   │
   └──> ExtensionRunner.emitBeforeAgentStart()
        └── auto-memory.ts appends "Memory Tool Usage"
        └── KẾT QUẢ: agent.state.systemPrompt (final)
```

### 📌 Thứ tự chính xác trong systemPrompt string

```
1. "You are an expert coding assistant..." (A)
2. "Available tools:" + brief snippets (B)
3. "Guidelines:" + guidelines (C)
4. "Pi documentation..." (D)
5. "# Project Context" + AGENTS.md content (E)
6. "Current date: ..." + "Current working directory: ..." (F)
7. "Memory Tool Usage:" + guidelines (G) ← append by extension
```

